data.description: Looking for a beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 bath home located in popular subdivision, Brighton Oaks? Look no more! This gorgeous home is convenient to 23rd St, Tyndall Air Force Base,Naval Support Activity Panama City and is walking distance to the highly desired North Bay Haven Charter Academy. This DR Horton, Cali floor plan boasts an open floor concept that includes a kitchen with a large island that opens into the living room and dining area. The Master bedroom has dual vanity sinks, a large tub, separate shower and a walk in closet. Enjoy the back yard which is equipped with a covered patio as well as a fully enclosed privacy fence for any furry family members. Remember; its all about LOCATION and it doesn't get much better than Brighton Oaks! Come view and take this beautiful home off the market today! (All sizes approximate and taken from public records, buyer to verify any details buyer deems important.)
